title: Immigrant To High End Client Acquisition With Marian V Esanu
itunes:title: Immigrant To High End Client Acquisition With Marian V Esanu
description:
Marian V Esanu is a immigrant who became a millionaire and the host of the High End Client Acquisition podcast. And today he is going to explain why most marketers fail because they don’t implement these principles in their marketing efforts.
 
Learn more about Underdog Empowerment here: https://underdogempowerment.com/106
